        {
            "id": "https://bluemap1e.github.io/2023/11/14/%E5%9C%A8Qt-Creator%E4%B8%AD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8OpenSSL/",
            "url": "https://bluemap1e.github.io/2023/11/14/%E5%9C%A8Qt-Creator%E4%B8%AD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8OpenSSL/",
            "title": "在Qt Creator中使用OpenSSL",
            "date_published": "2023-11-13T17:10:07.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"前言\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#前言\">#</a> 前言</h2>\n<p>最近在折腾 Qt，刚好可以做一些加解密的桌面应用来玩。因此就尝试在 Qt Creator 中集成 OpenSSL。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"环境\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#环境\">#</a> 环境</h2>\n<p><strong>OS</strong>: Windows 10/11</p>\n<p><strong>IDE</strong>: Qt Creator 11.0.3 (Open Source)\t下载链接：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucXQuaW8vZG93bmxvYWQtcXQtaW5zdGFsbGVyLW9zcz9oc0N0YVRyYWNraW5nPTk5ZDlkZDRmLTU2ODEtNDhkMi1iMDk2LTQ3MDcyNTUxMGQzNCU3QzA3NGRkYWQwLWZkZWYtNGU1My04YWE4LTVlOGE4NzZkNmFiNA==\">Download Qt OSS: Get Qt Online Installer</span></p>\n<p><strong>OpenSSL</strong>: OpenSSL 3.1.2 Win64\t\t 下载链接：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9zbHByb3dlYi5jb20vcHJvZHVjdHMvV2luMzJPcGVuU1NMLmh0bWw=\">Win32/Win64 OpenSSL Installer for Windows - Shining Light Productions (slproweb.com)</span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"qmake\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#qmake\">#</a> QMake</h2>\n<p>QMake 集成 OpenSSL 非常简单。</p>\n<p>新建 Qt 项目时选择 QMake，然后进入项目的 <code>.pro</code>  文件，添加这两行：</p>\n<p>（PS：把示例中的路径修改为你自己的 OpenSSL 安装路径）</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-qmake\">INCLUDEPATH += D:\\Lib\\OpenSSL-Win64\\include\nLIBS += -L&quot;D:\\Lib\\OpenSSL-Win64\\lib&quot; -lssl -lcrypto\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"cmake\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#cmake\">#</a> CMake</h2>\n<p>未完待续……</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "OpenSSL",
                "Crypto",
                "C++",
                "Qt"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://bluemap1e.github.io/2023/11/11/%E5%9C%A8Visual-Studio-2022%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AECrypto-%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/",
            "url": "https://bluemap1e.github.io/2023/11/11/%E5%9C%A8Visual-Studio-2022%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AECrypto-%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/",
            "title": "在Visual Studio 2022中配置Crypto++开发环境",
            "date_published": "2023-11-11T13:51:48.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"前言\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#前言\">#</a> 前言</h2>\n<p><code>Crypto++</code>  是一个轻量、开源、受欢迎的 <code>C++</code>  密码学库，采用了 OOP 的程序设计思想，总体比较契合 <code>C++</code>  的程序设计风格。</p>\n<p>本文主要介绍如何在 Visual Studio 2022 中配置 <code>Crypto++</code>  的开发环境。本文作者是个菜逼，失败了很多次，因此可能存在很多纰漏。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"环境\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#环境\">#</a> 环境</h2>\n<p><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10/11</p>\n<p><strong>IDE:</strong> Visual Studio 2022 (C++ SDK)</p>\n<p><strong>C++ 编译器:</strong> MSVC</p>\n<p><strong>Crypto++ 版本:</strong> Crypto++ 8.9.0</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"下载并解压crypto\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#下载并解压crypto\">#</a> 下载并解压 Crypto++</h2>\n<p>在 <code>Crypto++</code>  的官方网站可以下载 <code>Crypto++</code> ，选择自己想要使用的版本即可：</p>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY3J5cHRvcHAuY29tLyNkb3dubG9hZA==\">Crypto++ Library 8.9 | Free C++ Class Library of Cryptographic Schemes (cryptopp.com)</span></p>\n<p>下载后，把 <code>Crypto++</code>  的压缩包解压到自己想要存放 Crypto++ 的文件夹，这里要注意，压缩包没有内层文件夹，因此最好不要解压 <code>D:\\Download</code>  之类的目录下，否则容易造成混乱。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"编译crypto\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#编译crypto\">#</a> 编译 Crypto++</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"打开项目\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#打开项目\">#</a> 打开项目</h3>\n<p>进入 <code>Crypto++</code>  解压后的文件夹，找到 <code>cryptest.sln</code>  这个文件，双击用 Visual Studio 打开它。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"debug模式编译\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#debug模式编译\">#</a> Debug 模式编译</h3>\n<p>注意生成选项，对于 64 位系统建议选择 x64。先选择 Debug 模式。</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/2023/11/11/%E5%9C%A8Visual-Studio-2022%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AECrypto-%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/Options-1.png\" class title=\"Options-1\"></p>\n<p>在右侧的项目文件夹找到 <code>cryptlib</code> ，右键单击，生成：</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/2023/11/11/%E5%9C%A8Visual-Studio-2022%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AECrypto-%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/Cryptlib.png\" class title=\"Cryptlib\"></p>\n<p>Visual Studio 会尝试编译 <code>cryptlib</code> ，这个过程需要一点时间，可以在下方的控制台看到进度。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"release模式编译\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#release模式编译\">#</a> Release 模式编译</h3>\n<p>切换到 Release 模式。</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/2023/11/11/%E5%9C%A8Visual-Studio-2022%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AECrypto-%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/Options-2.png\" class title=\"Options-2\"></p>\n<p>在右侧的项目文件夹找到 <code>cryptlib</code> ，右键单击，生成。</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/2023/11/11/%E5%9C%A8Visual-Studio-2022%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AECrypto-%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/Cryptlib.png\" class title=\"Cryptlib\"></p>\n<p>Visual Studio 会尝试编译 <code>cryptlib</code> ，这个过程需要一点时间，可以在下方的控制台看到进度。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"编译完成\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#编译完成\">#</a> 编译完成</h3>\n<p>到这一步，编译已经完成了。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"配置visual-studio\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#配置visual-studio\">#</a> 配置 Visual Studio</h2>\n<h3 id=\"新建项目\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#新建项目\">#</a> 新建项目</h3>\n<p>可以新建一个项目用来测试，打开 Visual Studio，创建新项目，控制台应用。</p>\n<p>你可以先把这些代码复制到源文件中，以便测试：</p>\n<p>（代码来源：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY3J5cHRvcHAuY29tL3dpa2kvQWR2YW5jZWRfRW5jcnlwdGlvbl9TdGFuZGFyZA==\">Advanced Encryption Standard - Crypto++ Wiki (cryptopp.com)</span>）</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption data-lang=\"C++\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"cryptlib.h\"</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"rijndael.h\"</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"modes.h\"</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"files.h\"</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"osrng.h\"</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"hex.h\"</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;iostream></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;string></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> argc<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">char</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> argv<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"12\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"13\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> CryptoPP<span class=\"token punctuatio